songs.title: I lobe my wife
songs.lyrics:
Ooh i love my wife, i love my wife aahh!
Lets go ride a bike, with my wife aahh!
My wife is really young my wife is real small
Lets go to the beach and play with a beach ball
Praise Jesus, God, and my wife
Lets go to the beach and ride a bike
Ooh i love my wife, i love my wife aahh!
Lets go ride a bike, with my wife aahh!
